data.description: This home is ready for you to move in, Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom and a Flex is a true gem. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a landscaped yard. With no HOA fees, it offers you the freedom to enjoy your home without the additional cost. The floor plan is designed for both comfort and functionality, providing an ideal setting for families and entertainment alike. The main floor features a open floor plan with a formal dining area and the master bedroom. The other bedrooms are conveniently located on the upper level. The Master bath features a soaking tub with jets, walk in shower, double vanity and walk-in closet. The open kitchen is equipped with stainless appliances, beautiful cabinetry, large island and ample counter space. It flows seamlessly into the lining room area. Upstairs enjoy a dedicated space for entertainment and relaxation in your flex room. The two car garage has lots of storage and parking space for your vehicles. The backyard can be your own private oasis where you can unwind on the patio or explore your landscape possibilities. The location is so convenient, with Clear Creek military gate, Advent Hospital, Killeen Airport, Walmart, Fort Cavazos and various shopping centers all within a 5-minute drive. You have an elementary school and a middle school within walking distance.
